headline: David Solomon Praised Trump Accounts – Will Goldman Sachs Billions Follow?
summary: The Trump Account savings accounts created by the One Big Beautiful Bill Act in July represent a new federal push toward building generational wealth. These tax-deferred investment vehicles target newborns born between January 1, 2025, and December 31, 2028, seeding each eligible child’s account with a $1,000 government deposit.
